{"tid":2514686,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"何謂自愛 (Self-love) ？ 要愛人先愛自己？","createTime":"2021-05-03T12:04:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T22:23:38.000Z","uid":223963,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c709c25c02b5a4feaf7a47b89b82d2c01abe80cc","tid":2514686,"uid":223963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:04:34.000Z","msg":"最近同人傾開呢個話題<br />\n佢話自己做唔到self-love 所以唔會發展新關係<br />\n咁我個人嚟講都認同佢諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但又延伸到另一個問題 <br />\n喺關係之中Self-love是否必要條件？<br />\n因為我眼見其他咁多pair情侶，有啲拍咗好多年拖<br />\n但我唔覺得佢地全部每一個人都做到//甚至明白到咩叫自愛<br />\n雖然如此，但佢地都可以維持到一段好長好stable嘅關係<br />\n咁當然每段關係背後佢地都有自己方法去維繫<br />\n<br />\n另外我上網搵到啲人對self-love嘅定義<br />\n佢地話always choose yourself<br />\n咁我某程度上都認同嘅，但係如果係一段關係入面如果一個人每次都choose yourself<br />\n根本就唔會出現compromise // 接受對方唔同 // 磨合<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/61778138_1600760160056437_7297970229924069376_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=9267fe&amp;_nc_ohc=FsYnrS3JU5oAX-MRXN-&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=4eb85427a949943f0ed6e4158145b9a9&amp;oe=60B558A7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.6435-9%2F61778138_1600760160056437_7297970229924069376_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26ccb%3D1-3%26_nc_sid%3D9267fe%26_nc_ohc%3DFsYnrS3JU5oAX-MRXN-%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3D4eb85427a949943f0ed6e4158145b9a9%26oe%3D60B558A7&h=1721f693&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後我又搵吓啲人點樣界定自己做到self-love<br />\n有啲人就話 you don't need others to validate you, <br />\n唔洗靠人，只要靠自己，唔需要靠人地去感受愛 等等<br />\n所以講到self-love = self-independent咁<br />\n咁如果一個人可以做到咁獨立，咁又冇必要去進入一段關係<br />\n去同另一個人一齊生活呢？<br />\n另外，如果兩個同時都咁自愛咁獨立  唔需要他人肯定<br />\n咁又有冇需要對方嘅needs呢？<br />\n<br />\n我個人嚟講 我唔否定自愛喺個人發展到好重要 同埋自愛當然可以幫助到關係發展<br />\n但係，係咪啲人講到咁重要呢？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想聽吓大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />＝必然<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />＝ 不是必然"},{"pid":"c282d4156d2746a7f01ac29f413ebd8fc9b66ecf","tid":2514686,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:06:22.000Z","msg":"乜嘢叫love<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c25aba2db315abbe9d6722644154366106ef392","tid":2514686,"uid":223963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c282d4156d2746a7f01ac29f413ebd8fc9b66ecf","tid":2514686,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:06:22.000Z","msg":"乜嘢叫love<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:07:35.000Z","msg":"你呢個問題好複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0607669a05e2b854dbfc6adce28619ead29a7c","tid":2514686,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:12:46.000Z","msg":"又係啲女權撚發明出嚟嘅on9 term<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b314577efe5b8b0facce5a10d80220d36cf958","tid":2514686,"uid":233692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:18:15.000Z","msg":"側田都話:<br />\n不懂愛自己比自戀可悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba78ed5129a6528d10ec11678d619035ef5f275","tid":2514686,"uid":390009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c709c25c02b5a4feaf7a47b89b82d2c01abe80cc","tid":2514686,"uid":223963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T12:04:34.000Z","msg":"最近同人傾開呢個話題<br />\n佢話自己做唔到self-love 所以唔會發展新關係<br />\n咁我個人嚟講都認同佢諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但又延伸到另一個問題 <br />\n喺關係之中Self-love是否必要條件？<br />\n因為我眼見其他咁多pair情侶，有啲拍咗好多年拖<br />\n但我唔覺得佢地全部每一個人都做到//甚至明白到咩叫自愛<br />\n雖然如此，但佢地都可以維持到一段好長好stable嘅關係<br />\n咁當然每段關係背後佢地都有自己方法去維繫<br />\n<br />\n另外我上網搵到啲人對self-love嘅定義<br />\n佢地話always choose yourself<br />\n咁